<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是煙火大會，<delay8 />
我有個東西想在今天交給你！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你覺得是什麼呢？
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看！<delay frames="40" />是<colour id="1" />仙女棒<colour id="65535" />喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好啦，<delay20 />快收下吧。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種小型的煙火也很不錯呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就讓我們來炒熱氣氛吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />糟糕<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />偏偏這時候你的包包沒空位，<delay8 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒辦法再裝更多東西了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虧我興奮地喊出<delay8 />「你看！」<delay8 />啊<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等你把口袋騰出空位後，
記得跟我說一聲，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我到時候再把東西給你！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>